overview: Zoe models her new dress for Justine and Justine eagerly devours the dress and Zoe. Jayme returns to a second year of internship reporting to Ariel, only Ariel has more than just office stuff in mind. Samantha arrives home to find a note from her girlfriend Cindy with instructions to follow the rose petals to their bedroom.
tagline: Sit back and embrace the passion!
title: Intimate Invitation 11
